reviewText: The movies were just as described.  We enjoyed only one.  The others were not to our taste.  We're elderly and our tastes were shaped at an earlier time.
Title: Romantic Comedies - 6 Movie Set

reviewText: The movies arrived on time and in excellent shape. These are lighthearted stories just for being entertained. It is great to have all of them together and I am looking for other package deals of similar movies.
summary: A great collection....just fun and laughs.
Title: Romantic Comedies - 6 Movie Set

reviewText: Good Value, Good movies. I enjoyed them all. The convenience of having them in the same package and at a great price is very much appreciated. Thanks.
Title: Romantic Comedies - 6 Movie Set

reviewText: The sound tracks on 4 of the 6 movies were horried.  Sounded hollow and scratchy all the way through--or at least as far as I could take watching them.  I was going to return the disks but was told to keep them at no charge.
Title: Romantic Comedies - 6 Movie Set

reviewText: While I do not like to rate films as everyone has their own preferences....my main objectionis NOT the films but the packaging.When you buy movies in a set there is danger of one (in my case) coming loose and it wasso badly scratched from wiggling around the spindle that it could not be used.I gave the whole thing away after one film.
Title: Romantic Comedies - 6 Movie Set
